<h2 class="bold font-l">The Troll Market</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Behind a hidden door under the Brooklyn Bridge can be found the famed Troll Market: a meeting ground for supernatural beings from all over the world, it's possible to find almost anything here - from tooth fairies to magical artefacts. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Bizarre Bazaar</span> </h3>
